  "title": "Four people spotted several star-like UFOs above the airport in Montes Claros [2001]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/14/four-people-spotted-several-star-like-ufos-above-the-airport-in-montes-claros-2001/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-qZ",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JAN 3rd, 2001</strong>. Time: 9:30 pm. Duration: about 10 minutes. In Montes Claros, State of Minas Gerais, four witnesses observed several unidentified flying objects at an estimated altitude of 2,000 meters. The UFOs looked like red stars and were very close to each other, going down to the ground in vertical motion until they got close to the head 12 of the airstrip, in the northwest sector [of the Airport]. The objects remained stationary most of the time, but when they moved away, they did it at a high speed.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.591. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni em Montes Claros, Minas Gerais”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n",
